Maintainer: Björn Fisseler <bjoern.fisseler@gmail.com>
Description: A package for R that provides access to Moodle data for learning analytics, including the pseudonymization of personally identifiable information (PII).  
    'Moodle' is an open source Learning Management System (LMS) developed by MoodleHQ. For more information about Moodle, visit <https://moodle.org>.
